keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map m Marks.activateCreateMode swap
map ` Marks.activateGotoMode swap
map ! enterFindMode
unmap /
map g<home> firstTab
unmap g0
map g<end> lastTab
unmap g$
map sd visitPreviousTab
unmap ^
map q Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
unmap T
map gf LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map s LinkHints.activateMode
map f LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
map F LinkHints.activateModeToDownloadLink
unmap <a-f>
map zy LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl
unmap yf
map zj nextFrame
map zR mainFrame
unmap gF
map zh goPrevious
unmap [[
map zl goNext
unmap ]]
map Y duplicateTab
unmap yt
map < moveTabLeft
unmap <<
map > moveTabRight
unmap >>
map M toggleMuteTab
unmap <a-m>
map X closeTabsOnRight
map T restoreTab
unmap gt
unmap gT
unmap W
unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>
unmap gu
unmap gU
searchEngines:
